	   <tr><td colspan=2>good job picking ESK, we are by far the best looking charecters in the game, you should see full darkforge with ruby legs, <br>i chose one because of the challenge, and the rarity (having played a halfling druid to 45, big change of pace =)<br>anyway here are some tips:<br>get agility above 75, your AC drops radically after that,<br>AC is king, never ever forget this, choosing an ESK you obviously dont care too much about stats this is good,&nbsp;&nbsp;stats are over rated, they key to a good tank is not sacrificing AC for stats, example, use Jagged bands instead of Plat fire rings, use friking BRACERS not bracelets,  there is 25 raw ac right there.  Darkforge or even better ebony BP over mithreal, etc.  <br>but dont take my word for it, experiment<br><br>oh by the way the AC thing also applies to monsters, at 39 you get two spells shadowvortex and heartflutter which will drop a monsters AC drasticlly, using these two in everyfight (which you can with an ESK mana pool) and laugh as your group shreads your enemies<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
